==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Automorphic
<hw>Au`to*mor"phic</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Auto-</ets> + Gr. <?/ for, shape.]</ety> <def>Patterned after
one's self.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The conception which any one frames of another's mind is more or
less after the pattern of his own mind, -- is
<qex>automorphic</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>H. Spenser.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Automorphism</ent>⟦br⟧
